### Program/Course Management API Tests
### Server: http://localhost:3001

# ===========================================
# PROGRAMS
# ===========================================
@adminToken = ""
@programId = ""
@termId = ""
@levelId = ""
@venueId = ""
@hallId = ""
### Create Program
POST http://localhost:3001/api/programs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "English Multiverse",
  "code": "EM",
  "description": "English course for ages 11-17",
  "minAge": 11,
  "maxAge": 17
}

### Get All Programs
GET http://localhost:3001/api/programs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Program by ID
GET http://localhost:3001/api/programs/{{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update Program
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/programs/{{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated: English course for teenagers",
  "isActive": true
}

### Deactivate Program
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/programs/{{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

# ===========================================
# TERMS
# ===========================================

### Create Term
POST http://localhost:3001/api/terms
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "{{programId}}",
  "name": "Fall 2025",
  "startDate": "2025-09-01",
  "endDate": "2025-12-31",
  "isCurrent": true
}

### Get All Terms
GET http://localhost:3001/api/terms
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Filter Terms by Program
GET http://localhost:3001/api/terms?programId={{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get Current Term
GET http://localhost:3001/api/terms?isCurrent=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Update Term
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/terms/{{termId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isCurrent": false
}

